"title": "5832: desire",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5832: desire",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A sense of longing for or wanting something. It may be a positive or negative force in the human character, but sinful desire is characteristic of human nature and must be overcome by the believer. God also expresses desires in Scripture.</p>\n<h2>Righteous desire</h2>\n<h3>Desire for God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:25\">PSA 73:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:1-Ps42:2\">PSA 42:1–42:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps63:1-Ps63:8\">PSA 63:1–63:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps143:6\">PSA 143:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:8-Isa26:9\">ISA 26:8–26:9</a></p>\n<h3>Desire for right living</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:8\">PSA 40:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:174\">PSA 119:174</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:1\">PRO 22:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:18\">HEB 13:18</a></p>\n<h3>Desire for wisdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr1:7-2Chr1:12\">2CH 1:7–1:12</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:5-1Kgs3:14\">1KI 3:5–3:14</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:5\">JAS 1:5</a></p>\n<h3>Desire for spiritual gifts</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:1-1Cor14:5\">1CO 14:1–14:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:27-1Cor12:31\">1CO 12:27–12:31</a></p>\n<h3>Desire for church office</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:1\">1TI 3:1</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Sinful desire</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:21\">DEU 5:21</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:17\">EXO 20:17</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:6\">PRO 11:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:24\">ROM 1:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:8\">ROM 7:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:9-1Tim6:10\">1TI 6:9–6:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:13-Jas1:15\">JAS 1:13–1:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:3\">2PE 3:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:16-Jude1:18\">JUD 1:16–1:18</a></p>\n<h3>Sinful desire is inherent in human nature</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:3\">EPH 2:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:10\">2PE 2:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:18\">2PE 2:18</a></p>\n<h3>Following Jesus Christ means putting to death sinful desires</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:24\">GAL 5:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:5-Rom8:14\">ROM 8:5–8:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:11-Rom13:14\">ROM 13:11–13:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:22-Eph4:24\">EPH 4:22–4:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:5\">COL 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:22\">2TI 2:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:14-1Pet1:15\">1PE 1:14–1:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:11\">1PE 2:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:1-1Pet4:5\">1PE 4:1–4:5</a></p>\n<h2>The tension in believers between the desires of the old and new natures</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:16-Gal5:17\">GAL 5:16–5:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:18\">ROM 7:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:1\">JAS 4:1</a></p>\n<h2>Sexual desire</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:16\">GEN 3:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song7:10\">SNG 7:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:11\">1TI 5:11</a></p>\n<h3>Sinful lust condemned</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:28\">MAT 5:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:26\">ROM 1:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:3-1Thess4:4\">1TH 4:3–4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:3\">1PE 4:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:18\">2PE 2:18</a></p>\n<h2>God's desires</h2>\n<h3>God desires true worship</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:7\">MAT 12:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos6:6\">HOS 6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:13\">MAT 9:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:21-Amos5:24\">AMO 5:21–5:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:21-John4:24\">JHN 4:21–4:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:5-Heb10:14\">HEB 10:5–10:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:6-Ps40:8\">PSA 40:6–40:8</a></p>\n<h3>God desires right living</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:6\">PSA 51:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:19-Jas1:20\">JAS 1:19–1:20</a></p>\n<h3>God's desires for his people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:8\">2CH 9:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps132:13\">PSA 132:13</a></p>",
